<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Document type</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">Detailed guide</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">When to use</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
Use this pattern to tell users about changes to existing Tariff quotas and new Tariff quotas.
</p>

<div class="govuk-inset-text">
   The body of the Tariff quota notice must be an exact copy of the text that’s been provided (do not make any changes – it must match <a href="https://eur-lex.europa.eu/homepage.html" class="govuk-link">EU legislation</a>).
</div>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">How it works</h2>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Title format</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
Description (Tariff quota notice xx)
</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Collection page</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
Add the document to the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/tariff-quota-notices-2014" class="govuk-link">Tariff quota notices</a> document collection. Do not create a public change note.
</p>
